# PM Workflow

#### **React Native & Expo**

- [x]  Initialize **React Native project** (`expo init`)
- [ ]  Configure **Tailwind (NativeWind) for UI**
- [ ]  Build **navigation (React Navigation)**
- [ ]  Implement **loading states, error handling, and toasts**
- [ ]  Improve **responsiveness & animations**
- [ ]  Test on **physical devices (iOS & Android)**
- [ ]  Deploy beta version via **Expo Go or TestFlight**

#### **Supabase (Authentication & Database)**

- [ ]  Set up **Supabase (Auth, Database, Edge Functions)**
- [ ]  Implement **user authentication** (Google/Email login)
- [ ]  Capture and **store metadata** in Supabase
- [ ]  Implement **background API calls** (fetch metadata from Supabase)
- [ ]  Store past detections in a **history/log** for users

#### **Object Detection & Machine Learning**

- [ ]  Install **TensorFlow.js** (for local ML inference)
- [ ]  Research and select a **pre-trained PyTorch model** (COCO-SSD or custom)
- [ ]  Load **TensorFlow.js object detection model**
- [ ]  Integrate **Expo Camera API**
- [ ]  Run inference on camera feed and **display detected objects**
- [ ]  Optimize performance (adjust **frame rate**, **model size**)
- [ ]  Process detection results to **filter out noise** (e.g., confidence > 50%)
- [ ]  Reduce app size by **optimizing ML models & assets**

#### **FastAPI Backend (Optional for Server-Side Inference)**

- [ ]  Set up **FastAPI backend**
- [ ]  If using **server-side inference**, connect to FastAPI ML backend
- [ ]  Backend **handles image processing**

#### **UI/UX Improvements**

- [ ]  Design **core screens** (Home, Camera, Results, Profile)
- [ ]  Create a rough **wireframe for UI improvements**
- [ ]  Refine **UI styling (Tailwind, animations)**
- [ ]  Add a **settings screen** for user preferences

#### **Performance & Optimization**

- [ ]  Improve **camera performance** (reduce lag, optimize detection)
- [ ]  Improve **responsiveness & animations**
- [ ]  Optimize **ML model size & assets**

#### **Deployment & Testing**

- [ ]  Conduct **bug fixes & testing** (device compatibility)
- [ ]  Implement **push notifications (optional)**
- [ ]  Deploy beta version via **Expo Go or TestFlight**

